{"tid":2124302,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"關稅華參與APEC視像會議　譴責貿易分化政策促保持邊界開放","createTime":"2020-07-25T09:49:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-25T10:08:47.000Z","uid":51271,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"6efffd76d3d45f5bf101e9180b6fd1acbf71a4b0","tid":2124302,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T09:49:35.000Z","msg":"關稅華終於o係腐乳樽爬出黎<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20200725/s00001/1595663967281/%e9%82%b1%e9%a8%b0%e8%8f%af%e5%8f%83%e8%88%87apec%e8%a6%96%e5%83%8f%e6%9c%83%e8%ad%b0-%e8%ad%b4%e8%b2%ac%e8%b2%bf%e6%98%93%e5%88%86%e5%8c%96%e6%94%bf%e7%ad%96%e4%bf%83%e4%bf%9d%e6%8c%81%e9%82%8a%e7%95%8c%e9%96%8b%e6%94%be\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20200725%2Fs00001%2F1595663967281%2F%25e9%2582%25b1%25e9%25a8%25b0%25e8%258f%25af%25e5%258f%2583%25e8%2588%2587apec%25e8%25a6%2596%25e5%2583%258f%25e6%259c%2583%25e8%25ad%25b0-%25e8%25ad%25b4%25e8%25b2%25ac%25e8%25b2%25bf%25e6%2598%2593%25e5%2588%2586%25e5%258c%2596%25e6%2594%25bf%25e7%25ad%2596%25e4%25bf%2583%25e4%25bf%259d%25e6%258c%2581%25e9%2582%258a%25e7%2595%258c%25e9%2596%258b%25e6%2594%25be&d=jSYRdVihxMCX8m9Ry8wFHTcyzTZykTUlxRhnZlW9F%2Bg%3D&h=913ff7d9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20200725%2Fs00001%2F1595663967281%2F%25e9%2582%25b1%25e9%25a8%25b0%25e8%258f%25af%25e5%258f%2583%25e8%2588%2587apec%25e8%25a6%2596%25e5%2583%258f%25e6%259c%2583%25e8%25ad%25b0-%25e8%25ad%25b4%25e8%25b2%25ac%25e8%25b2%25bf%25e6%2598%2593%25e5%2588%2586%25e5%258c%2596%25e6%2594%25bf%25e7%25ad%2596%25e4%25bf%2583%25e4%25bf%259d%25e6%258c%2581%25e9%2582%258a%25e7%2595%258c%25e9%2596%258b%25e6%2594%25be&h=5be3d80a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20200725/s00001/1595663967281/%e9%82%b1%e9%a8%b0%e8%8f%af%e5%8f%83%e8%88%87apec%e8%a6%96%e5%83%8f%e6%9c%83%e8%ad%b0-%e8%ad%b4%e8%b2%ac%e8%b2%bf%e6%98%93%e5%88%86%e5%8c%96%e6%94%bf%e7%ad%96%e4%bf%83%e4%bf%9d%e6%8c%81%e9%82%8a%e7%95%8c%e9%96%8b%e6%94%be</a><br />\n<br />\n商務及經濟發展局長邱騰華今日（25日）參與亞太經濟合作組織（APEC）首個以視像形式舉行的貿易部長會議，他指出，新型冠狀病毒引發的連串貿易限制無助控制疫情，貿易是解決目前問題的關鍵良方，不應視為問題所在，他譴責所有帶歧視和分化的政策措施，並促請所有經濟體在此關鍵時刻保持邊界開放，維持供應鏈的暢順運作，避免建立貿易壁壘或採取不理性的貿易政策。<br />\n<br />\n邱騰華強調，香港作為世界貿易組織的創始成員和獨立的關稅區，一直支持自由市場政策，不斷推動貿易自由化。任何不必要的貿易限制和保護主義措施在此緊要關頭，都只會加重疫情，對區內的長遠復蘇帶來沉重打擊。"},{"pid":"cc1c40e654eccb1d6da84fcb62207d7daadc4e58","tid":2124302,"uid":11148,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T09:52:48.000Z","msg":"仲獨立關稅區<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n真係謊言講100次連自己都信撚埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a991227f494286660dc1dd650a03b284d6994822","tid":2124302,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T09:54:36.000Z","msg":"圍威喂<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b591727aca9b8dc5f31cf05d093ed266a242e09","tid":2124302,"uid":267494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T09:56:06.000Z","msg":"facebook, google, ebay, amazing<br />\nam i a joke to you? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"703c494bc0f916a9310ad7a536e48b133ef11658","tid":2124302,"uid":241399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T09:59:11.000Z","msg":"感覺中國屬意既人會做到 WTO 新主席（宜家果個做到八月底）<br />\n然後美國搵幾個大國重新建立一個新組織"},{"pid":"c345f7c3abc717989ab950b4adebe5045a3f2ab4","tid":2124302,"uid":7369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T09:59:34.000Z","msg":"【內地疫情速遞】內地增34宗確診 深圳、珠海暫停香港互認隔離醫學觀察<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n本港周五新增123宗確診個案，再創新高之際，深圳市人民政府口岸辦公室周六零時發出公告，按省疫情防控工作統一部署，已暫停實施深港互認隔離醫學觀察政策，在香港完成強制檢疫14天隔離後24小時內入境來深人員，入境後需接受14天隔離醫學觀察，呼籲位旅客提前做好安排。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200725/M62OJMMNRLRUHA6R6I4TNGBEKA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200725%2FM62OJMMNRLRUHA6R6I4TNGBEKA%2F&d=jSYRdVihxMCX8m9Ry8wFHTcyzTZykTUlxRhnZlW9F%2Bg%3D&h=e72a6b1a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200725%2FM62OJMMNRLRUHA6R6I4TNGBEKA%2F&h=d545439f\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200725/M62OJMMNRLRUHA6R6I4TNGBEKA/</a><br />\n<br />\n講條撚咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36f1c24dec523673e767a899d0e33fb7827f72f0","tid":2124302,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"703c494bc0f916a9310ad7a536e48b133ef11658","tid":2124302,"uid":241399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T09:59:11.000Z","msg":"感覺中國屬意既人會做到 WTO 新主席（宜家果個做到八月底）<br />\n然後美國搵幾個大國重新建立一個新組織"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T10:08:47.000Z","msg":"同WHO一"}]}